full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/10/2023 CHECK APPLICABLE ITEM AND INSERT REQUIRED ADDED INFORMATION I have been granted an extension of temporary stay by the office of the Immigration and Naturali- zation Service at (Location of office) The extension will expire on .
